- `rbrKnowledgeSoundness` involves `Verfier.KnowledgeStateFunction` and `Extractor.RoundByRound`

The core idea is that the one-shot version is a special case of the general version. The general version allows for an arbitrary `WitMid` and `Extractor.RoundByRound`, while the one-shot version uses a specific structure. To bridge this, we need to show that the one-shot structure is compatible with the general definition.

